        <p class="metadata">Posted by Benoît Durand (intiilapa) on 2011-10-08T11:03:34.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>A unit test validates the behavior. I think it's more a concern of configuration or documentation: you must use shortname for a *name like formatterName.</p>

<p>Try this :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
resources.log.AppLog.writerParams.formatterName = "Simple"
</code></pre>

<p>Be careful to use the info parameter with this formatter. If you have a log without extra, your file write without interpretation <em>%info%</em>.</p>

